---
/**
 * Services section focused on outcomes and delivered impact.
 */
---

<section id="services" class="section" data-reveal>
  <div class="space-y-10">
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <p class="eyebrow">Services</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold sm:text-4xl">Outcomes over deliverables.</h2>
      <p class="max-w-3xl text-lg text-muted">
        Engagements are built for traction: tighten the operating system, surface the real levers, and
        make every iteration measurable.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
      <article class="card" data-reveal>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Fractional leadership</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-muted">
          Step in as a strategic engineering partner, aligning product, ops, and finance while building
          a delivery cadence that lasts beyond the engagement.
        </p>
      </article>
      <article class="card" data-reveal>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Data infrastructure</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-muted">
          Replace fragile pipelines with reliable, observable data systems that unlock forecasting,
          cohort analysis, and operational truth.
        </p>
      </article>
      <article class="card" data-reveal>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">RCM optimization</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-muted">
          Diagnose leakage across the revenue cycle, automate the highest-friction steps, and rebuild
          workflows so every dollar has a clear path.
        </p>
      </article>
      <article class="card card-accent" data-reveal>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Experimentation</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-muted">
